messages.message:
Hi Brian, you seem to be a good fit for an opening we have at our new start up... please let me know if you are interested in chatting. Best, Darren

https://govadvance.recruiterbox.com/jobs/fk0mpno
I don't have the Akka and Java experience but I have everything else and the nice-to-haves credentials.
Hi Brian, we can work with that ... if you are interested please apply to the recruiterbox app online and my CTO and I can schedule a chat with you soon... what is your availability for work?
I just got the fun job at swiftpage but I like talking to people. I can go through the process if you think it will help.
Also it does say 1099 and I have evidence that I can do 2 things at a time. Not at the same time but without scheduling conflict.
I think its still worth a chat ... that is what I was thinking too that perhaps you could do this part time and see how it works out
What is your availability for a quick chat today or tomorrow morning?
Any time after 5 today or 8ish tomorrow 4804660856
Ok so after 4pm AZ time... I will call you from my mobile 480-203-7559. Thanks!
Oh I meant AZ time. I forgot time just changed.
Also can you send your resume to me at Darren.cummings@solidintelligence.com ahead of our call
Haha yeah, like gandalf. Sent the resume
Haha yeah, like gandalf. Sent the resume

Brian, thanks for sending your resume... I am forwarding to my CTO. Instead of a call tonight I am going to have him review first and have a more targeted conversation. Let's shoot for early next week as I am headed north tomorrow to get some final skiiing in!
